kpi_info.title: TRANSFERRED DATA FOR NRT DCH UL
kpi_info.use: The amount of data transferred in NRT DCH in uplink direction during measurement interval, excluding HS-DSCH return channels. The counter is updated at 20 second intervals or when the connection is released or when active set is changed.
